sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Route as POST /matches
    participant Controller as MatchGameController@store
    participant Match as MatchGame
    participant Stats as LeagueStatsService
    participant Players as Participant model
    participant Cache as Dashboard / Stats cache

    User->>Browser: Fill in match form
    Browser->>Route: Submit new match result
    Route->>Controller: Call store(request, leagueStats)
    Controller->>Controller: Validate input

    alt Validation fails
        Controller-->>Browser: Redirect back with errors
    else Validation passes
        Controller->>Match: Create match record
        Controller->>Stats: recalculateParticipantStats()
        Stats->>Players: Reset and recalculate standings
        Players-->>Stats: Updated points, wins, losses
        Stats-->>Controller: Standings updated
        Controller->>Cache: Clear dashboard and stats cache
        Controller-->>Browser: Redirect to dashboard with success message
    end